=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold\">Safe Meeting Locator</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-1\">Find verified safe meeting spots near you for secure in-person exchanges.</p></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-5\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-wallet h-5 w-5 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M19 7V4a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H5a2 2 0 0 0 0 4h15a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v4h-3a2 2 0 0 0 0 4h3a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-2a1 1 0 0 0-1-1\"></path><path d=\"M3 5v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h15a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold\">Wallet Access</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-1\">Manage your wallet, send and receive payments via Paystack from your phone.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 md:py-20 bg-primary/5 border-y\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 max-w-xl text-center\"><div class=\"h-14 w-14 rounded-2xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-bell h-7 w-7 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10.268 21a2 2 0 0 0 3.464 0\"></path><path d=\"M3.262 15.326A1 1 0 0 0 4 17h16a1 1 0 0 0 .74-1.673C19.41 13.956 18 12.499 18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 4.499-1.411 5.956-2.738 7.326\"></path></svg></div><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Get Notified on Launch Day</h2><p class=\"text-muted-foreground 